MR A-Eng. SB 1594
1 SECTION 2. Notwithstanding any other provision of Oregon law, all state and local law
2 enforcement agencies in this state shall cooperate with any federal immigration authority,
3 as defined in ORS 180.805, in carrying out any action concerning any person convicted of a
4 crime constituting a felony under Oregon law.
5 SECTION 3. This 2026 Act being necessary for the immediate preservation of the public
6 peace, health and safety, an emergency is declared to exist, and this 2026 Act takes effect
7 on its passage.
